    "84114292": {
      "title": "Experimental evidence of a relationship between turnip yellow mosaic virus and wild cucumber mosaic virus",
      "abstract": "Abstract A serological relationship has been found between turnip yellow mosaic virus and wild cucumber mosaic virus, viruses which are not known to have any common host plant. Similarities in the physicochemical properties and the morphology of these two viruses are remarked upon and comments are made on the possibility of grouping plant viruses on the basis of such affinities."
